        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2240285188" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1988683987804372672">This book was much better than I expected. I was worried I might find his commentary about the Spanish to be condescending and insulting. Happily that was not the case. There was a perfect balance of pointing out the seemingly bizarre and the seemingly amazing of a different culture without laying anything on too thick. I&apos;m Spanish-born, half Spanish, half American, and have lived as an expat for the last 13.5 years in two different countries. I could relate to many of their experiences and it b</span>
  <span id="freeText1988683987804372672" style="display:none">This book was much better than I expected. I was worried I might find his commentary about the Spanish to be condescending and insulting. Happily that was not the case. There was a perfect balance of pointing out the seemingly bizarre and the seemingly amazing of a different culture without laying anything on too thick. I'm Spanish-born, half Spanish, half American, and have lived as an expat for the last 13.5 years in two different countries. I could relate to many of their experiences and it brought back a lot of memories of past adventures. I won't continue the series but it was an enjoyable light read. </span>
  <a data-text-id="1988683987804372672" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
